Tidak.

62
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,630
Ke tepi, puan.

63
00:09:28,666 --> 00:09:29,996
Syabas,

64
00:09:30,083 --> 00:09:33,793
anda telah menghentikan mesin pembunuh
yang ulung iaitu Vacuubot.

65
00:09:33,875 --> 00:09:37,375
